    public abstract class EditActivity
extends ThemedActivity
    EditActivity is a base class that provides support for various configuration editing activities.

        protected void clearNameIfNecessary(android.widget.EditText nameText,
                                    DeviceConfiguration device)
        This gets called if we're changing a device, so if the nametext was "NO DEVICE ATTACHED", it should now be empty for editing. Otherwise, it should be the name of the device.
        Parameters:
        nameText - - the name field that may need to be "cleared"
        device - - the module
